name: Dominic Winkle 3/100
description:
These 3D Dorki's are limited to 100 and come in various edition sizes based on how cool they are, the more awesome they are the lower the edition size.  

The original (Ethereum) collection can be found on OpenSea & Nifty Gateway: 
https://opensea.io/collection/dorkisofficial
https://niftygateway.com/marketplace?collection=0x0588a0182ee72f74d0ba3b1fc6f5109599a46a9c&niftyType=1
www.wearedorkis.com
www.dorkiville.com
https://discord.gg/dorkis

These re-creations are done under Non-Exclusive Licence featuring original hand drawn (using pencil and paper) artwork by Tori Batt @NFTtori
